{"tid":822287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風山竹】中國氣象局稱港珠澳大橋可抗強風　橋上83人留守","createTime":"2018-09-16T09:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T09:30:21.000Z","uid":49391,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0b967d3f7704d349831b58505c2fd7d409d07c56","tid":822287,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1869071/org/aeeed3216821c6c42786d379eb8a5d84.jpg/kvSa3_m6SIMK-_qqtFxxRjLiI1wTrEuZGhGXmhoRl5o?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1869071%2Forg%2Faeeed3216821c6c42786d379eb8a5d84.jpg%2FkvSa3_m6SIMK-_qqtFxxRjLiI1wTrEuZGhGXmhoRl5o%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=ce969196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超強颱風「山竹」直撲廣東，各方關注港珠澳大橋只能預防16級颱風，或未能抵受最高風力達17級的「山竹」，網上更一片大橋可能在強風下倒塌的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國氣象局透過官方微博澄清道，「山竹」略過呂宋島後，風力已削弱為15级，港珠澳大橋有能力抵擋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1868914/org/1c141f7dd439c03cca317abbbd6278cb.jpg/0XL51eZkJOm8mGoQ5aEta7gLarKw4F4Wns1B6p7NQeo?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1868914%2Forg%2F1c141f7dd439c03cca317abbbd6278cb.jpg%2F0XL51eZkJOm8mGoQ5aEta7gLarKw4F4Wns1B6p7NQeo%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=1c5225b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國氣象局稱，「山竹」穿過菲律賓，進入南海區域時，風力已削弱為15級。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\n中國氣象局在其官方微博刊文指，「山竹」在登陸菲律賓時的風力為17級，但距離中國尚有一段距離，當時港珠澳大橋並未受到相關影響。而「山竹」穿過菲律賓後，因呂宋島的高山導致其結構被破壞，進入南海區域時，風力已削弱為15級。<br />\n<br />\n根據中央氣象台最新預報結果，港珠澳大橋所在區域將於颱風登陸前遭遇最大風力，大約14級至15級左右。<br />\n<br />\n中國氣象局又引香港路政署副署長徐永華表示，港珠澳大橋設計採取了相當高的標準，並通過風洞測試，具備足夠的抗風能力和較高的安全系數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n非值守人員已全部撤離<br />\n<br />\n早在昨日（15日）下午8時，港珠澳大橋管理局已啟動Ⅰ級響應。目前橋上留守值守人員83人（其中東島21人，西島31人，收費樓、救援樓及養護樓共31人），主要為監控、養護、收費、救援、路政、用電及排水保障人員。非值守人員已於15日下午7時全部撤離至安全場所。<br />\n<br />\n另據廣東海事局消息，為保障港珠澳大橋安全，目前其橋區水域上下三海里之內船隻已清空，保持安全距離。在其附近亦已安排兩艘大馬力拖輪，做貼身保護。以防止一旦有個別船舶走錨時能及時處理，避免其撞向大橋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/236129/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F236129%2F&d=oKxhwpfRMxZjXWLFL2Yh9hFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=7815ec82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/236129/</a>"},{"pid":"a429b5473287b886680b7650b8aeaf50fe499f33","tid":822287,"uid":146588,"like":6,"dislike":16,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"連登仔又輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a8df5d3e68bf5a9c5d9f3bb4787a5b358e8af4","tid":822287,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"「山竹」在登陸菲律賓時的風力為17級，因呂宋島的高山導致其結構被破壞，進入南海區域時，風力已削弱為15級。"},{"pid":"674b8eff80a69031fbebbb6033428ea43ec075be","tid":822287,"uid":29270,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a429b5473287b886680b7650b8aeaf50fe499f33","tid":822287,"uid":146588,"like":6,"dislike":16,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"連登仔又輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:10:16.000Z","msg":"個風唔爭氣關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56a1fc12cb7a16512ec1a209093454c7d84161f","tid":822287,"uid":9286,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"聽日新聞 83人下落不明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cc474e7410eb9032872e7fa7cf24a32300252d","tid":822287,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"黨會保佑你"},{"pid":"c9a406342e445120701227077f7fc359fe8e0a65","tid":822287,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a429b5473287b886680b7650b8aeaf50fe499f33","tid":822287,"ui